          "detail": "In pyproject.toml: move litellm (line 34), typer (line 35), platformdirs (line 36) from core dependencies to an optional extras section (e.g., [project.optional-dependencies] mini-swe = ['litellm>=1.75.5', 'typer', 'platformdirs']). The mini-swe-agent/ directory is empty (confirmed: ls shows only . and ..) and no files import these packages. This reduces the default install footprint.",
