          "detail": "In pyproject.toml: both 'httpx' (line 19) and 'requests' (line 23) are core deps. Requests is used in browser_tool.py (line 63), agent/model_metadata.py (line 14), and tests. The issue said 'consolidate httpx usage' \u2014 but requests is legitimately used in sync contexts (browser_tool.py, model_metadata.py). This step is LOW PRIORITY: check if browser_tool.py and model_metadata.py could be migrated to httpx or if requests should stay. Do not consolidate unless it reduces net complexity \u2014 keeping both is fine if the usage patterns differ (sync vs async).",
